items.content_text:
### Algorithms and Data Structures

*   [Decompress (‚≠ê117)](https://github.com/mirage/decompress) - A pure OCaml implementation of Zlib.
*   [Ke (‚≠ê51)](https://github.com/mirage/ke) - Fast implementation of queue (FIFO) in OCaml.
*   [Duff (‚≠ê20)](https://github.com/mirage/duff) - Implementation of Rabin's fingerprint and delta compression by P. MacDonald in OCaml (same as [libXdiff](http://www.xmailserver.org/xdiff-lib.html)
